there's only one dominant coalition.

00:21:23.140 --> 00:21:24.720
That reflects the character
of your consciousness.

00:21:24.720 --> 00:21:27.280
By and large, you're only
conscious of one or two things

00:21:27.280 --> 00:21:28.113
