sometimes bizarre conditions

00:31:49.890 --> 00:31:52.450
but that tell you a lot
about consciousness.

00:31:52.450 --> 00:31:54.590
So, for example, for the prosopagnosia,

00:31:54.590 --> 00:31:56.660
you're unable to see a face.

00:31:56.660 --> 00:31:59.070
So the patient says, well, I can see,

00:31:59.070 --> 00:32:00.453
and they're different forms of it,

00:32:00.453 --> 00:32:02.060
I can see your mouth,

00:32:02.060 --> 00:32:03.130
