holistic, gestalt-like,

00:32:22.970 --> 00:32:23.803
as a lot of people think.

00:32:23.803 --> 00:32:26.290
In this case, there's
actually discrete foci.

00:32:26.290 --> 00:32:29.180
There are a bunch of
neurons that code for faces,

00:32:29.180 --> 00:32:31.000
that code for the conscious
perception of the faces.

00:32:31.000 --> 00:32:32.577
